thread.title_full: Quality Logo Products, Inc. reviewed by Guido Lamonaca

author: Guido Lamonaca
title: Guido Lamonaca
text: My son wanted a burlap koozie to give away at his upcoming wedding. I found Quality Logo Products on an internet search. They have exceeded my expectations from price to delivery. Doc, the Account Executive was overly helpful with the art work and layout. I WILL order from this company again!
